{"type": "article", "id": 37398, "title": "这些寿司巧克力，你猜是什么味？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-03T02:03:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 14275, "name": "Kit Kat"}, {"id": 37271, "name": "Mitab"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 37272, "name": "Better Shelter"}, {"id": 21691, "name": "DAVID BOWIE"}, {"id": 37273, "name": "Brad Ascalon"}, {"id": 37274, "name": "Noreen Loh Hui Miun"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 119, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170202221644nqtcG5iV243fIgv0.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Better Shelter</h3><p>由伦敦设计博物馆设立的年度设计奖 Beazley Design of the year 最近公布了 2016 年的得主：瑞典公司 <a href=\"http://www.bettershelter.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Better Shelter</a> 推出的同名模块化避难所。Better Shelter 成立于 2010 年，由宜家旗下专门负责人道主义公益活动的 <a href=\"http://www.ikeafoundation.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">IKEA Foundation</a> 资助，也是联合国难民署的合作机构，旗下的避难所已经进驻了多个国家的难民营。和其它临时避难设施相比，Better Shelter 胜在它的简洁、轻便和长达 3 年的耐久。它不需要任何特殊装备即可由 4 人在 4 到 8 小时内完成组装或者拆卸，内部的空间最多可容纳一个五口之家居住。每一间所含的模块包括窗户、蚊帐、通风系统以及固定在屋顶的太阳能板等，全部由轻质的塑料和金属制成，分别装在两个 80 kg 重的平板包装盒中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221744nDgVqfwRdaLNBHOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702022217442VTMfCGRxPZscJv5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221746cZm79SDnTidrlaC1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.884000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221745z1RGl6IQrVUWkYag.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.231193\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>KitKat Sushi by Kit Kat</h3><p>很快就是情人节了，日本各大巧克力品牌也陆续公布了限定款。不过今天介绍的 KitKat Sushi 或许更有愚人节的节日气氛：日本 <a href=\"https://nestle.jp/brand/kit/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kit Kat</a> 将去年愚人节开的玩笑做成了货真价实的巧克力，以庆祝 2 月 2 日在东京银座开张的专卖店。尽管以寿司为名，它们的噱头也仅限于造型，覆盆子（金枪鱼）、南瓜布丁（海胆）和甜瓜配奶酪（玉子烧）的口味并不猎奇。<a href=\"http://bg-mania.jp/2017/01/30190202.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">自 2 月 2 日到 2 月 4 日</a>，这三款巧克力将作为赠品赠予在店内消费超过 3000 日元的前 500 位顾客。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221721CtYXy8AL20q1WcbT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663814\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221721bHQfGeFtjZc28KMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.572127\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221723O6urYTDxSdGgs185.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684597\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221721HV5qKRo2TEJZ1Ihz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>David Bowie’s stamps by Royal Mail</h3><p>为了纪念去年逝世的 David Bowie，恰逢 Bowie 的第一张专辑问世 50 周年，英国皇家邮政（<a href=\"http://www.royalmail.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UK Royal Mail</a>）首次单独以一位文化界人士为主题推出了两组共计十张邮票。在这十张邮票中，六张采用的是经典专辑的封面，另外四张则是演唱会时的照片。它们将于 3 月 14 日正式销售，你可以通过<a href=\"http://shop.royalmail.com/issue-by-issue/david-bowie/icat/davidbowie\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>进行预订。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702022218073GWch561IFkpQlie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221806qvXB9lAcpyUHbRD4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900822\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702022218069hW01CjuFK4kcsUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900822\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221808s5YaPDxiz03MJFgK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900822\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221806DIChfPxcrigduTEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900822\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FLOAT by Wang Min</h3><p>这些由不同颜色组成、像是糕点一样的肥皂其实是新加坡设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/wangmin\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wang Min</a> 制作的概念品牌 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41951345/FLOAT\" rel=\"nofollow\">FLOAT</a>，她希望通过富有艺术感的设计吸引年轻的消费者，让肥皂在不使用的时候也能变成一件放在浴室里的装饰品。Min 设计的外包装仅由一张纸折叠而成，顾客可以通过正面透明的塑料覆膜直观地看到产品。纸张正面的图案和肥皂相对应，介绍则统一印在内侧，让整个设计显得更加环保。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221826ARkMVjwD0bI4zPJn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221826SOUoh5L4bHVZMzdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221825bJ2zhvOij9sRUNIc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702022218255XlR9G82meDVArQo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221826Rk4fHc0xZvi7UQTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ascent by Brad Ascalon</h3><p>在候车或者候机厅这样的公共区域，所使用的椅子似乎都比较单调，有些设计也不能满足类似充电这样的新式需求。为了让这些歇脚处变得美观实用，来自美国纽约的 <a href=\"http://www.bradascalon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brad Ascalon</a> 为瑞典设计品牌 <a href=\"http://mitab.se/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mitab</a> 打造了这款名为 Ascent 的模块化座椅系统。座椅贴着木胶合板制成的底座边缘放置，曲线和直线的组合形成了鲜明的视觉反差，看上去简洁优雅。每个单元最多可以容纳四个座椅，表面采用的织物也可以根据需要定制颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221844odNzsjKkZv8Ie4VW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221844MzE9evhZgFqulRsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221844uA597whnGvobSVgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667901\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221845n5e19zGB3xbfqA4i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Marriage by Noreen Loh Hui Miun</h3><p>这套名为 The Marriage 的雕塑是马来西亚裔设计师 <a href=\"http://miun.sg/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Noreen Loh Hui Min</a> 的作品，擅长花艺的她把来自真实世界的植物和纸雕融合在一起。在作品外加上的玻璃罩子，一方面是考虑到它们本身的脆弱，另一方面则营造出了标本的感觉，就像在展示收集自童话世界的奇异生物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221953PSLrM4dgAY6zHXe9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221952cYwUFWeBztO7VRgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221952gifDFzAQnqueYExO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221952tpAiXcmj58lnhTQs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170202221953p3yclJ6Wx8PrCB7D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}